title: Gold Taco
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican
description: Vegetarian and vegan Mexican food from cerviche to tacos that are on soy or gluten version of meat tacos (al pastor, chorizo, bistecca, carnitas), plus pozole, tamales, veggieburgers, and veggie hotdogs. Offers a 4-course lunch special 13:00-18:00 for around 55 pesos with bread or tortilla, half a liter of special juice, non-gelatin dessert. There is a connected health food store that sells fake meat products.
streetAddress: Av. Eugenia 1558, e/ Tajín y Petén, Col. Narvarte M
